10
00:00:53,760 --> 00:00:56,360
The Community Health Action in Seclin

11
00:00:56,560 --> 00:00:58,880
is about working with residents,

12
00:00:59,080 --> 00:01:01,760
to start from the ground, from their needs.

13
00:01:01,760 --> 00:01:07,800
The idea is to bring residents together to discuss an issue that affects them

14
00:01:08,000 --> 00:01:15,000
and look for tools to deal with the problems they raise.

15
00:01:20,400 --> 00:01:25,440
The workshop starts with a moment to socialise informally

16
00:01:25,640 --> 00:01:27,200
over a coffee or a tea.

17
00:01:27,200 --> 00:01:33,080
It's a moment to talk with the others about what's on your mind.

18
00:01:33,080 --> 00:01:36,080
Then we get down to business :

19
00:01:36,280 --> 00:01:44,120
group work, voice and theatre exercises...

20
00:01:44,320 --> 00:01:49,040
Depending on the input of the participants, 

21
00:01:49,480 --> 00:01:53,160
we develop sketches,

22
00:01:53,480 --> 00:01:58,920
work on a theme we want to explore.

23
00:02:00,920 --> 00:02:09,480
Our task will be to develop a sketch about some sort of addiction.

24
00:02:11,000 --> 00:02:14,280
Ok, so a computer addict.

25
00:02:16,800 --> 00:02:20,440
It's not about exposing your private life any old how,

26
