I work ! 

36
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:52,240
I like this workshop. 

37
00:02:52,360 --> 00:02:57,200
It has helped me in my relationships to others.

38
00:02:57,200 --> 00:03:00,560
We learn so much from one another.

39
